data.text:
August 19, 2016

Brickleberry Armoogeddon Part 1 aka Season 4 is....

Brickleberry Armoogeddon Part 1 aka Season 4 is.... Hypocritical! I was trying to get a physical copy when the preorder was up on the dynamite website , but never went through. So I was very and I mean very happy to see the Amazon carrying the digital comic for a $1.99 . Which is a dollar to two dollars less than what you would pay for physical copy of the first edition .

I love that it starts off as season four right after the last episode ended Urian with the mad Max type of futuristic end of the world vibe . I appreciate the fact that everything is censored end the way the show should've been when you bought it digitally your devices, and/or DVD when it was a television show. And not censored . Anyways I cannot wait till the 30th for issue number two to come out along with three and four
